# Contributing to Canary

Thank you for your interest in contributing to Canary ‚Äî a privacy-first release mechanism for sensitive information.

We welcome contributions from developers, researchers, designers, writers, and privacy advocates. Whether it's fixing a bug, suggesting a feature, improving documentation, or contributing to our mission ‚Äî you're in the right place.

